Package edu.brown.cs.smayfiel.bacon

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Entity
    This interface is implemented by both Actors and Movies so they can both be stored in the IDCache.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Actor
    Class that contains an Actor.
    DatabaseHandler
    The DatabaseHandler is responsible for getting a connection to the database and then giving it to whomever needs it.
    IDCache
    This class is just a wrapper for a HashMap that caches all Actors and Movies seen so far.
    InputHandler
    This class takes the arguments from Main, parses them, calls Dijkstra, and then prints the results to the terminal.
    Main
    Main class just accepts the arguments and creates an InputHandler to deal with them.
    Movie
    The Movie class holds a single Movie.
